帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton) 和梅根·特雷纳 (Meghan Trainor) 宣布“真正标志性”合作“Chasin” https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-and-meghan-trainor-announce-truly-iconic-collab-chasin-3773436?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=paris-hilton-and-meghan-教练宣布真正的标志性合作追逐Surej SinghWed, 10 Jul 2024 05:39:03 +0000 Music NewsNewsPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3773436 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕丽斯·希尔顿和梅根·特雷纳的合成图像" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>希亚联合制作</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-and-meghan-trainor-announce-truly-iconic-collab-chasin-3773436">帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton) 和梅根·特雷纳 (Meghan Trainor) 宣布“真正标志性的”合作“Chasin”</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="帕丽斯·希尔顿和梅根·特雷纳的合成图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/paris-hilton">帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/meghan-trainor">梅根·特雷纳 (Meghan Trainor)</a>联手打造“真正标志性”的合作项目，名为“Chasin”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/steve-aoki-paris-hilton-lighter-interview-3517182">史蒂夫·青木和帕丽斯·希尔顿向我们讲述新合作“Lighter”——以及扔蛋糕</a></strong></li></ul><p>希尔顿和特雷纳在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-news/paris-hilton-meghan-trainor-announce-collab-chasin-1235055440/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>采访时宣布了这首新单曲，该单曲将出现在希尔顿<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-announces-details-of-second-album-infinite-icon-3761311">即将推出的第二张专辑“Infinite Icon”</a>中。这首歌曲将于 7 月 26 日发行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-to-release-new-album-executive-produced-by-sia-3517198">由 Sia 联合制作</a>。</p><p>特雷纳透露，她“几年前就开始写这首歌，并且知道我必须把它保存给一个非常特别的人。巴黎将其提升到了一个全新的水平。我不敢相信我能和她成为朋友。”</p><p>帕丽斯补充道：“[梅根]用语言表达了对我来说非常真实的经历；在你生命中的那个时刻，你找到了自信、力量和自爱，摆脱有毒的关系，继续你的生活。” </p><figure id="attachment_3761390" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3761390" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3761390" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/paris-hilton-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="帕丽斯·希尔顿.图片来源：Michael Buckner/WWD，来自 Getty Images" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/paris-hilton-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/paris-hilton-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/paris-hilton-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/paris-hilton-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/paris-hilton-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/paris-hilton-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3761390" class="wp-caption-text">帕丽斯·希尔顿.图片来源：Michael Buckner/WWD，来自 Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>特雷纳还谈到了她与希尔顿的关系：“她是我一直需要的妹妹，当她叫我姐姐时，我内心幸福得要死。我们一起创造了一些真正具有标志性的东西，这对我来说是一个愿望清单上的梦想成真。”</p><p> “Infinite Icon”将于 9 月 6 日通过希尔顿自己的制作公司 11:11 Media 发行，并由 Sia 担任执行制作。</p><p>这张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-paris-hilton-and-rina-sawayamas-slick-new-single-im-free-3767886">已经与泽山里奈 (Rina Sawayama) 合作的一首单曲“I&#39;m Free”进行了预览</a>。 《Infinite Icon》是希尔顿 2006 年首张专辑《Paris》发行 18 年后推出的，其中收录了她迄今为止最热门的歌曲《Stars Are Blind》。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-new-album-oasis-wonderwall-2157273">她第一次提到在 2017 年制作第二张专辑</a>，告诉<em>《时代》杂志</em>，这张专辑的灵感来自于“深屋、科技流行和电子流行”的声音。</p><p>这位流行文化偶像和社交名流暗示她将于 2022 年 12 月在音乐界回归，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-shares-new-version-of-00s-hit-stars-are-blind-3373048">她于 2022 年 12 月重新发行了首张单曲，现名为“Stars Are Blind（巴黎版）”。</a>她通过演唱这首欢快的流行歌曲进一步预告了自己的回归。与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/miley-cyrus">麦莉·赛勒斯 (Miley Cyrus)</a>和流行音乐制作人 Sia 一起参加赛勒斯在时代广场举行的除夕音乐会。 </p><figure id="attachment_3620019" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3620019" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3620019" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/paris-hilton-sia-@-2000-x-1270.jpg" alt="帕丽斯·希尔顿和希亚。照片来源：新闻界/Sia 提供" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/paris-hilton-sia-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/paris-hilton-sia-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/paris-hilton-sia-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/paris-hilton-sia-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/paris-hilton-sia-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/paris-hilton-sia-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3620019" class="wp-caption-text">帕丽斯·希尔顿和希亚。照片来源：新闻界/Sia 提供</figcaption></figure><p>希尔顿最近推出的其他单曲包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-paris-hilton-team-up-with-kim-petras-to-revamp-stars-are-blind-3451089">Kim Petras</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-paris-hilton-team-up-with-kim-petras-to-revamp-stars-are-blind-3451089">的《Stars Are Blind（巴黎版）》混音版</a>和 EDM 驱动的《Hot One》。</p><p> 2023 年 10 月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/steve-aoki-paris-hilton-lighter-interview-3517182">希尔顿接受<em>NME</em>采访，谈论了她这张专辑背后的创作过程。</a> “音乐一直是我生活的重要组成部分，”她开始说道。 “我喜欢在世界各地打碟，喜欢在最大的音乐节上打碟，喜欢举办音乐会，但唱歌是我真正喜欢做的事情，我很自豪能在录音室里工作。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paris-hilton-and-meghan-trainor-announce-truly-iconic-collab-chasin-3773436">帕丽斯·希尔顿 (Paris Hilton) 和梅根·特雷纳 (Meghan Trainor) 宣布“真正标志性的”合作“Chasin”</a>后，首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
