42.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/cocteau-twins@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cocteau-twins">Cocteau Twins</a>宣布重新发行他们与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/harold-budd">Harold Budd</a>合作的 1986 年专辑《月亮与旋律》——了解更多信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/stop-making-sense-tribute-talking-heads-3757341">在 Talking Heads 的致敬专辑“Stop Making Sense”中：“音乐是如此引人注目”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这张专辑经过重新制作，并将自 1986 年发行以来首次以黑胶唱片形式重新发行。除了以黑胶唱片形式重新发行外，《月亮与旋律》还将以 CD 格式和数字格式提供。该作预计于 8 月 23 日发售，现已可<a href="https://shop.4ad.com/release/463804-cocteau-twins-and-harold-budd-the-moon-and-the-melodies-2024-remaster?ffm=FFM_e4d83bdb9355983bdb306f5e0fab31b5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">通过 4AD 预订</a>并<a href="https://cocteautwins.4ad.co/moonmelodies" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在数字平台上预存</a>。</p><p>专辑的重新制作由乐队的 Robin Guthrie 监督，使用了项目录制过程中的原始磁带。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C9NF1B0Cnfh/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"